ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx3</blockquote><br />\nX4</blockquote><br />\nx5</blockquote><br />\n呢個仲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962d716a08d8cf3d578f6351735c20f8bf6285c2","tid":110554,"uid":3162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇錯以為中意一個人都要扮無野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx3</blockquote><br />\nX4</blockquote><br />\nx5</blockquote><br />\n呢個仲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家就係呢個情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744867b1d013ea3274c8e10e43364605a73f4b88","tid":110554,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T19:23:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇錯以為中意一個人都要扮無野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx3</blockquote><br />\nX4</blockquote><br />\nx5</blockquote><br />\n呢個仲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家就係呢個情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主有無考慮轉話題"},{"pid":"f8287294267feb733952113ab8b79314ab66f781","tid":110554,"uid":1274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T19:34:50.000Z","msg":"有，已經唔睬佢了，價值觀相差甚遠，廢事見親佢都想嘔！<br />\n我扮咗一排無嘢，扮得好辛苦，依家唔撚扮，直接等反面！"},{"pid":"0d6e4d2c741968f7bb1770c1859f73411f17bc95","tid":110554,"uid":15411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T19:47:50.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申，返左3年工，同事嚟。佢仲當我好好朋友添"},{"pid":"0920f04818399da4414b08697bc1a9da030d2746","tid":110554,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T19:53:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>返學啲group mates<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n某程度上仲要同佢地互相依賴<br />\n但關係真係「同學」僅此<br />\n 稱唔上朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁還好啦 唔熟本身都<br />\n我係明明係朋友 <br />\n但其實唔中意咁</blockquote><br />\nYes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 讀U三年日日一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實麻麻地佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e923f02177473a0e76076f9c0bc1bb2e9a172a","tid":110554,"uid":39508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:44:48.000Z","msg":"無辦法<br />\n出來做野更加要演好場戲<br />\n邊個首先忍唔住就會輸做衰人<br />\n最多人buy就係偽善扮無辜撚<br />\n你eq低d開人波做小家野輸左到時人地鍾意點玩就點玩<br />\n到時你跪哂地叩哂頭人地真係有排笑<br />\n所以幾唔妥人都要忍<br />\n人地做主動出手先就佢蝕底"},{"pid":"6ada9ab1708f2417aedb8956f0d50fd66c737920","tid":110554,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T10:51:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75ebf28b428a908ee3187f9b01d54d94ee8d1a5f","tid":110554,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:18:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d127e30a2a00f517a2ed825eb049bc4dc9bdb20e","tid":110554,"uid":37948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:24:29.000Z","msg":"YNWA"},{"pid":"0f9b75c899fadeb45a980e4652ba0c31efde557d","tid":110554,"uid":6688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:27:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dff27d4d4ce0c2acb01400f6a2e45dbfd9080a0d","tid":110554,"uid":82989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02